headlines.description: Aston Villa recovered from the sacking of Steven Gerrard with a 4-0 win.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ings nets brace as rampant Aston Villa rout Brentford 4-0

headlines.shortLinkText: Newcastle into fourth with win over Tottenham
